=====================================================================
TVGL Changes to Clipper 
=====================================================================
The goal has been to keep Clipper mostly identical to the version provided
by the author, Angus Johnson 
http://www.angusj.com/delphi/clipper.php

In order to simplify the TVGL API, the following lines of code have been changed:
#1. The following classes, structs, and enums at the following line numbers were
    changed from "public" to "internal": 70,130,214,353,424,443,444,450,452,453,
	455,456,458,479,486,546,1357, 4432